metadata.name: The Sahara Desert
metadata.description:
Everyone knows that the Sahara is the largest desert on earth. It is uniquely attractive, but all the while destructive. While I had seen photographs of dunes before, when in the desert, I fell into a sandstorm and felt the full power of Mother Nature. The Sahara struck me with its power and danger.

4000 x 2250

This is 1 of 7 limited NFT.
